# Core Deque Concepts

You’ll repeatedly see these operations:

---

## Remove expired elements

```java id="f7p1w5"
if (dq.peekFirst() < i) {
    dq.pollFirst();
}
```

---

## Remove useless smaller elements

```java id="n2x8k4"
while (!dq.isEmpty() && arr[dq.peekLast()] < arr[j]) {
    dq.pollLast();
}
```

---

## Add current element

```java id="c9v4m7"
dq.offerLast(j);
```

